		<a name="top" id="top"></a>
		<div id="siteNotice"><script type='text/javascript'>if (wgNotice != '') document.writeln(wgNotice);</script></div>		<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading">Mnemonic dominic system</h1>
		<div id="bodyContent">
			<h3 id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</h3>
			<div id="contentSub"></div>
									<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="#searchInput">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->
			<p>The <b>mnemonic dominic system</b> is a mnemonic system similar to the <a href="/wiki/Mnemonic_major_system" title="Mnemonic major system">mnemonic major system</a>, but much shorter. It was invented by <a href="/wiki/Dominic_O%27Brien" title="Dominic O'Brien">Dominic O'Brien</a>, who uses it to perform feats such as memorizing the order of a deck of <a href="/wiki/Playing_cards" title="Playing cards" class="mw-redirect">playing cards</a> in under a minute.</p>
